npm install ag-grid-angular ag-grid-community


‚∏ª

üìÅ Step 2: File Structure Overview

src/
 ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ app/
      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ grid/
      ‚îÇ    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ grid.component.ts
      ‚îÇ    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ grid.component.html
